\par \hich\af1\dbch\af28\loch\f1 It is proposed for DMAware that separa\hich\af1\dbch\af28\loch\f1 
tely-distributed derived works must be distinctly identified in a way that avoids all possibility of confusion with the original work or subsequent versions of that work, and that provides a source for the original as well as the derived work.
