There will be a libra\hich\af1\dbch\af28\loch\f1 ry-level open-source license, comparable in strength to the GNU Lesser General Public License [}{\field\fldedit{\*\fldinst {\f1\fs20 \hich\af1\dbch\af28\loch\f1  \hich\af1\dbch\af28\loch\f1 HYPERLINK
