\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f1\fs20 The library-level open-source license permits use of the library in construction of system elements without requiring the resulting combination to be open-source.\~ 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Derivative works of the open-source library are still required to be preserved as open-source software. 
